msgstr "Talk_Phone_st"

msgctxt "5684"
msgid "Hana"
msgstr "Hana"

msgctxt "5688"
msgid "Akiyama"
msgstr "Akiyama"

msgctxt "5692"
msgid "Talk_Phone_ed"
msgstr "Talk_Phone_ed"

msgctxt "5696"
msgid "dummy"
msgstr "dummy"

msgctxt "5700"
msgid "Police Officer"
msgstr "Policía"

msgctxt "108_Hana"
msgid "Boss! "
msgstr "¡Jefe! "

msgctxt "120_Akiyama"
msgid "Whoa! What's wrong, Hana-chan?"
msgstr "¡Ey! Hana-chan ¿qué paso?"

msgctxt "132_Hana"
msgid "What's wrong!? You mind explaining that forex contract that arrived in the office!? "
msgstr "¿Que qué pasa? ¡¿Me podrías explicar como llego un contrato forex a la oficina?!\n"\n"(NT: Contrato Forex es para intercambiar divisas)"

msgctxt "144_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, uh... that. I went to this free investment seminar recently and it looked like a good deal. So, I thought I'd invest a million or so. "
msgstr "Oh, eh... Eso. Fui a un seminario de inversión gratuita hace poco y parecía un buen trato. Entonces, pensé en un invertir un millón más o menos."

msgctxt "156_Hana"
msgid "Are you out of your mind!? Did you even read the contract? It's a complete scam! "
msgstr "¡¿Te estás escuchando?! ¿Leíste el contrato? ¡Es una estafa en toda regla!"

msgctxt "168_Hana"
msgid "I canceled it immediately! You know, I just can't believe you sometimes, boss! "
msgstr "¡Apenas llego lo rechacé de inmediato! ¡Jefe, ande con más cuidado!"

msgctxt "180_Akiyama"
msgid "You're really something, Hana, you know that? What would I do without you? Hahaha. "
msgstr "Que haría sin ti, Hana-chan jajaja."

msgctxt "192_Hana"
msgid "You can't sweet-talk your way out of this one! Just don't be such a big idiot next time! "
msgstr "¡No me hables con cariño después de lo que te salve! ¡Eres un idiota SHUN AKIYAMA!"

msgctxt "204_Akiyama"
msgid "Sorry... "
msgstr "Lo siento."

msgctxt "264_Akiyama"
msgid "(Ouch. That was rough...) "
msgstr "(Mierda... ya estoy muerto.)"

msgctxt "336_Akiyama"
msgid "Hello?"
msgstr "Oi."

msgctxt "348_Police Officer"
msgid "Hi, this is Officer Sasaki from the Kamurocho Police Department. Am I speaking to Shun Akiyama-san? "
msgstr "Buenas, Soy el oficial Sasaki del departamento de Policía de Kamurocho. ¿Estoy hablando con Shun Akiyama-san?"

msgctxt "360_Akiyama"
msgid "That's me. "
msgstr "Asi es."

msgctxt "372_Police Officer"
msgid "You signed a foreign exchange contract with a company called Ciel Trading, is that correct? "
msgstr "Dígame, ¿usted firmó un contrato con una empresa llamada Ciel Trading?"

msgctxt "384_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, uh, yes... Yes, I did. "
msgstr "Eh, uh, sí... Sí, lo firme, ¿paso algo?"

msgctxt "396_Police Officer"
msgid "Well, I'm calling to let you know they've been arrested for illegal business practices. "
msgstr "Bueno, lo llamaba para hacerle llegar la noticia que fueron arrestados por prácticas comerciales ilegales."

msgctxt "408_Akiyama"
msgid "What? "
msgstr "¡¿Eh?! "

msgctxt "420_Police Officer"
msgid "I'm in the process of calling potential scam victims we found in their client list. "
msgstr "Estamos en proceso de llamar a las todas la víctimas de esta estafa, su número estaba en la lista de clientes."

msgctxt "432_Police Officer"
msgid "You're really lucky we arrested them before they actually got any money out of you. "
msgstr "Fuiste muy afortunado. Los arrestamos antes que te roben todo tu dinero."

msgctxt "444_Talk_Phone_st"
msgid "Your contract was for a million yen, but don't worry. It's null and void. "
msgstr "El contrato que firmo por un millón de yenes ya se encuentra nulo y sin efecto."

msgctxt "456_Akiyama"
msgid "I see... "
msgstr "Oh, bien gracias, Oficial Sasaki-san."

msgctxt "468_Police Officer"
msgid "Just remember, if something sounds too good to be true, it probably is. "
msgstr "Recuerde. Si algo suena muy bueno para ser verdad, probablemente no lo sea."

msgctxt "480_Akiyama"
msgid "Got it. "
msgstr "Entendido."

msgctxt "492_Police Officer"
msgid "All right, then. I'll call you again once we know more. "
msgstr "Bien, entonces... Te llamaré devuelta si pasa algo más."

msgctxt "504_Akiyama"
msgid "Okay, thanks. "
msgstr "Bien, Gracias Oficial."

msgctxt "564_Akiyama"
msgid "(Man, talk about getting lectured. At least Hana-chan didn't hear about it. That would've been brutal.) "
msgstr "(Mierda, habla de sermones... Menos mal Hana-chan no se enteró. Eso hubiera sido el fin...)"

